{title: We Bring The Sacrifice Of Praise}
{subtitle: Kirk Dearman}
{key: F}
{tempo: 96}
{keywords: Mod. Apo. Fast}
{time: 4/4}





[F]We bring the sacrifice of praise 
into the [Bb]house of the [F]Lord,
[F]We bring the sacrifice of [F]pr[Dm]aise 
Into the [F/C]house [C7]of [F7]the [F]Lord,
And we [Bb]offer up to [F]You 
the sacri[Gm]fices [C7]of thanks[F]giving, [F7/A]
And we [Bb]offer up to [F]Y[Dm]ou 
The sacri[Gm]fi[F/C]ces [C7]of [F]praise






